msgstr "Bitte fülle alle Pflichtfelder* aus."

#: build/contact-form/render.php:143 src/contact-form/render.php:143
msgid ""
"By using this form, you consent to the storage and processing of your data "
"through our website. Additional information can be found in our privacy "
"policy on <a href=\"#\" id=\"privacy_policy_url\">Datenschutzerklärung</a>."
msgstr ""
"Mit der Nutzung dieses Formulars erklärst du dich mit der Speicherung und "
"Verarbeitung deiner Daten durch diese Website einverstanden. Weitere "
"Informationen findest du in unserer <a href=\"#\" "
"id=\"privacy_policy_url\">Datenschutzerklärung</a>."

#: build/contact-form/render.php:166 src/contact-form/render.php:166
msgid "submit"
msgstr "absenden"

#: functions/contact-form.php:36
msgid "Form not sent. Captcha wrong. Please try again."
msgstr ""
"Das Formular konnte nicht abgesendet werden. Das Captcha ist ungültig. Bitte "
"probier es erneut."

#: functions/contact-form.php:64
msgid "Thank you. The form has been sent."
msgstr "Vielen Dank. Deine Nachricht wurde verschickt."

#: functions/contact-form.php:95
msgid "New Message from"
msgstr "Neue Nachricht über"

#: functions/contact-form.php:111
msgid "Your Message on"
msgstr "Deine Nachricht über"

#: build/contact-form/index.js:115 src/contact-form/edit.js:88
#: build/contact-form/index.js:88
msgid ""
"The receiver address may be altered within the Sunflower theme settings. By "
"default, emails are sent to the site administrator."
msgstr ""
"Die Empfänger*innen-Adresse kann in den Sunflower-Einstellungen geändert "
"werden. Standardmäßig wird das Formular an den*die Webseiten-"
"Administrator*in gesendet."

#: build/contact-form/index.js:118 src/contact-form/edit.js:96
#: build/contact-form/index.js:96
msgid "Title of the form"
msgstr "Titel des Formulars"

#: build/contact-form/index.js:123 src/contact-form/edit.js:108
#: build/contact-form/index.js:108
msgid "Mail To"
msgstr "Empfänger-E-Mail"

#: build/contact-form/index.js:124 src/contact-form/edit.js:109
#: build/contact-form/index.js:109
msgid "Mail form to this address instead of default receiver."
msgstr "Sende Formular an die angegebene Adresse statt dem Standard-Empfänger."

#: build/contact-form/index.js:126 src/contact-form/edit.js:114
#: build/contact-form/index.js:114
msgid "default receiver"
msgstr "Standard-Empfänger"

#: build/contact-form/index.js:130 src/contact-form/edit.js:122
#: build/contact-form/index.js:122
msgid "Require E-Mail"
msgstr "E-Mail ist Pflichtfeld"

#: build/contact-form/index.js:134 src/contact-form/edit.js:131
#: build/contact-form/index.js:131
msgid "Send confirmation to sender"
msgstr "Bestätigung an den Absender schicken"

#: build/contact-form/index.js:135 src/contact-form/edit.js:135
msgid ""
"This only sends a short confirmation that the form was submitted "
"successfully. No user content will be included. It is recommended to use a "
"ticket system for detailed confirmations."
msgstr ""
"Dies versendet nur eine kurze Bestätigung über den erfolgreichen Versand des "
"Formulars. Es werden keine Benutzereingaben übertragen. Für detailliertere "
"Bestätigungen wird die Nutzung eines Ticket-Systems empfohlen."

#: build/contact-form/index.js:139 src/contact-form/edit.js:144
#: build/contact-form/index.js:144
msgid "Display Phone Field"
msgstr "Telefon-Feld anzeigen"

#: build/contact-form/index.js:143 src/contact-form/edit.js:153
#: build/contact-form/index.js:153
msgid "Require Phone"
msgstr "Telefon ist Pflichtfeld"

